en: Installtion Directory of the Steam version of DELTARUNE
A patched version detected.\nIs game updated or only patch updated?
zh_CN: 检测到打了补丁的版本。\n是游戏更新了还是只是补丁更新了？
zh_TW: 偵測到打了補丁的版本。\n是遊戲更新了還是只是補丁更新了？

en: Please go to Steam and right click DELTARUNE in your game library\nProperties...→Installed Files→Verify integrity of game files\nThen back to here for patch after verified.
zh_CN: 请打开 Steam 并在你的库中右键 DELTARUNE\n属性...→已安装文件→验证游戏文件的完整性\n等待验证完成后回来安装补丁
zh_TW: 請打開 Steam 並在你的收藏庫中右鍵 DELTARUNE\n內容...→已安裝檔案→驗證遊戲檔案的完整性\n等待驗證完成后回來安裝補丁

en:
DELTARUNE Chinese Patcher By SheepYhangCN
Made with Godot Engine 4.1.1 .NET
DELTARUNE Chinese Localized Version by 好人汉化组

Set the installtion directory of the Steam version of DELTARUNE
Patcher will automatically patch data.win of every chapter

This patcher is open source on Github
Click to open Github repository
zh_CN:
DELTARUNE 汉化安装器 By 憨憨羊の宇航鸽鸽
